column7: Auctioneer's copy, Annot. with prices and names
Auctioneer's copy, annot. with all buyers and prices.  There is also a list of sellers, indicating how the profits were to be distributed.
Auctioneer's copy.  Not annot. excepting two title changes and six added lots.
Sans annotation. Appartenait probablement au marchand J.B.P. Lebrun.
